data.description: Gorgeous Froehlich 4 bedroom plus office and possible 5th bedroom is within walking distance of the Seven Oaks Country Club and golf course! The expanded Grand Cayman plan offers a potentially separate guest suite layout, with kitchenette hook-ups. Generous and gracious in every way, you will love the large open kitchen with abundant counter space and storage. Richly appointed, this home features a brick facade and entry, and s stone patio overlooking the gorgeous pool and spa. The wonderful primary bedroom suite features a romantic tile fireplace, sumptuous travertine bathroom, and a stunning organized closet. Rhe west wing could eaaily be cloaed off for a rental or maybe ADU. Hardwood flooring, plantation shutters, elegant light fixtures and drapes, and a 3 car garage top it all off, and make this the home you have been waiting for.! Book your appointment today!
